rows.label: qst200918_msg001
rows.name: We're back!

rows.label: qst200918_msg002
rows.name: Oh, you're back, young lady!

rows.label: qst200918_msg003
rows.name:
Thanks to you, we can reopen
the shop. Thank you!

rows.label: qst200918_msg004
rows.name:
Not at all... I haven't
done anything special.

rows.label: qst200918_msg005
rows.name:
I'm happy just knowing that
everyone can be happy.

rows.label: qst200918_msg006
rows.name:
You really are a good
kid, young lady...

rows.label: qst200918_msg016
rows.name:
As thanks, I'll let you have
some freshly baked, warm
Lucky Sachiveria Bread!

rows.label: qst200918_msg017
rows.name: Wow! Really?!

rows.label: qst200918_msg018
rows.name:
I'm so happy! I feel
so happy right now!

rows.label: qst200918_msg019
rows.name:
To have you say that makes
me, the baker, happy too!

rows.label: qst200918_msg007
rows.name: Ehehe...

rows.label: qst200918_msg008
rows.name:
Hey, you lot... You
should be careful, mo.

rows.label: qst200918_msg009
rows.name:
If you're with that woman,
disaster will strike soon, mo.

rows.label: qst200918_msg010
rows.name:
Kasane must be placed at
the top of the Nopon Commerce
Guild's blacklist, mo!

rows.label: qst200918_msg011
rows.name:
Ah, Kupon-san, thank you
for your hard work! You've
been through a lot.

rows.label: qst200918_msg012
rows.name: Mo mo mo... Whose fault do you think...

rows.label: qst200918_msg013
rows.name:
If you're ever in trouble
again, please let me know!

rows.label: qst200918_msg014
rows.name:
M-mo mo mo... With such a
cheerful response, I'm at
a loss for words, mo...

rows.label: qst200918_msg015
rows.name:
I'm starting to mistakenly
think that Kasane isn't the
one spreading misfortune, mo...

rows.label: qst200918_msg020
rows.name:
What are you saying, Kupon-san?
Of course I'm not the one
spreading misfortune.

rows.label: qst200918_msg021
rows.name:
That's right. There's no way such a
nice girl would spread misfortune.

rows.label: qst200918_msg022
rows.name: M-mo mo mo...

rows.label: qst200918_msg023
rows.name: I'm speechless, mo...

rows.label: qst200918_msg101
rows.name:
Driver-san, do you think
many people became happy
because of this incident?

rows.label: qst200918_msg102
rows.name:
I think so. I believe everyone
became happy, one way or another.

rows.label: qst200918_msg103
rows.name:
But it seems like a lot of
unfortunate events happened
one after another...?

rows.label: qst200918_msg104
rows.name:
Well, yeah. I think everyone
barely became happy.

rows.label: qst200918_msg105
rows.name:
But you know, a lot of
unfortunate events did
happen one after another.

rows.label: qst200918_msg106
rows.name:
Indeed. Thanks to Kasane's
efforts, everyone managed
to become happy somehow.

rows.label: qst200918_msg107
rows.name:
But it is concerning that
so many unfortunate events
occurred in succession.

rows.label: qst200918_msg108
rows.name:
Yeah. Thanks to Kasane, everyone
probably became a little happier.

rows.label: qst200918_msg109
rows.name:
But still, unfortunate events
do pile up. That was a bit
unnatural, wasn't it?

rows.label: qst200918_msg110
rows.name:
You're right... Is it because
my power is still immature?

rows.label: qst200918_msg111
rows.name: M-maybe so...

rows.label: qst200918_msg112
rows.name: M-maybe...

rows.label: qst200918_msg113
rows.name: M-maybe so...

rows.label: qst200918_msg114
rows.name: Well, I dunno...

rows.label: qst200918_msg115
rows.name:
I have to work harder so that
even more people can be happy!

rows.label: qst200918_msg116
rows.name:
Yeah, we'll be counting on
you from now on, Kasane.

rows.label: qst200918_msg117
rows.name:
Yeah, we'll be counting on
you from now on, Kasane.

rows.label: qst200918_msg118
rows.name:
Yeah, we'll be counting on
you from now on, Kasane.

rows.label: qst200918_msg119
rows.name:
You got it, we'll be counting
on you from now on, Kasane.
